      • action

        public void action()
        This method tries to achieve all subgoals of the SequentialGoal to be achieved sequentially. If one of the subgoals fail, it stops the plan body execution.
        Specified by:
        action in class jade.core.behaviours.Behaviour

      • onStart

        public void onStart()
        Initializes this plan. Starts the goals iterator and verifies if the goal that triggered this plan body execution is a SequentialGoal. If not, it throws an IllegalArgumentException.
        Specified by:

      • setNextGoal

        protected void setNextGoal(Goal previousGoal,
                           Goal goal)
                    throws ParameterException
        Sets the parameters of the next goal to be executed based on the previous goal execution. It should be overridden by subclass of goals are not annotated with the Parameter annotation.
        Parameters:
        previousGoal - the previously executed goal.
        goal - the goal that is going to be dispatched.
        Throws:
        ParameterException - if an error occurred during setting up the next goal.
